name: Levon MOORE, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent of the State Correctional Institution at Graterford, The District Attorney of the County of Philadelphia, Respondent

parties: Levon MOORE, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent of the State Correctional Institution at Graterford, The District Attorney of the County of Philadelphia, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 22nd day of August, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus Ad Subjiciendum and Application for an Immediate Hearing are denied.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
